    schema1:description "John has been an integral part of our Geological Disposal Facility (GDF) programme since 2016. Before joining the programme, John was in the Royal Navy with a 30 year nuclear engineering career as a submariner. In his last Defence role he was the UK’s Director of Nuclear Propulsion; responsible for all aspects of designing, delivering and supporting a fleet of submarine reactor plants."@en ;
